    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface AsDoubleStreamPlus
extends AsDoubleStreamPlusWithCalculate, AsDoubleStreamPlusWithCollect, AsDoubleStreamPlusWithConversion, AsDoubleStreamPlusWithForEach, AsDoubleStreamPlusWithGroupingBy, AsDoubleStreamPlusWithReduce, AsDoubleStreamPlusWithStatistic
    Classes implementing this interface can provider a StreamPlus instance of itself.

    NawaMan -- nawa@nawaman.net
